name: semicolon
description:
About 4 months ago, there was a strange incident at home when the family was gathering.
Father, brother, nephew all possessed including me. believe it or not but this incident is really real.
and Since then I have felt uncomfortable being at home, as if someone was always watching. and it interfered with my mental health, so I was always anxious, afraid of the dark, even afraid of knives. and this video is a collection of pictures I made from that story, depicting my scary house.
